  "encoding": "windows-1252",
  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table bordercolor=\"#000080\">\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> <strong>Times'\n        ruins</strong></font><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p><font>In <em>The Education of Henry Adams</em>,\n        Adams discusses what time's ruins, of Rome in particular,\n        have taught him: </font>\"Young men as a rule saw\n        little in Italy, or anywhere else, and in after life,\n        when Adams began to learn what some men could see, he\n        shrank into corners of shame ....\" Burbank\n        experiences a similar learning process, albeit a literary\n        one.</p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td>What Burbank learned</td>\n<td><a href=\"Stones_JR.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Education_HA.htm\">Adams' <em>Education</em></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Education_HA.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Romance vs Realism</td>\n<td><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>the first draft</td>\n<td><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>structural analysis</td>\n<td><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"IMG_Rialto1988.htm\"><img src=\"../images/pic.gif\"/></a><a href=\"IMG_StMark.htm\">\n                St. Mark &amp; Winged Lion</a></td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><font>back to \"Burbank\"</font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
  "text": "Times' ruins In The Education of Henry Adams , Adams discusses what time's ruins, of Rome in particular, have taught him: \"Young men as a rule saw little in Italy, or anywhere else, and in after life, when Adams began to learn what some men could see, he shrank into corners of shame ....\" Burbank experiences a similar learning process, albeit a literary one. reference topics What Burbank learned Adams' Education Romance vs Realism the first draft structural analysis St. Mark & Winged Lion back to \"Burbank\"",
